race.description: Global Lubricant Distributor Country Boosted Handicap
race.comment: DO IT FOR YOU (4) recorded a strong on-pace win here last time when resuming over this trip. Kept fresh with 37 days in between and can repeat the dose. IT'SALLSAIDANDONE (8) improved sharply last start but found one better at Murwillumbah, beaten a head. Genuine hope if she can hold that form. GAMING (3) never stopped trying first-up at Grafton but was just denied at long odds. Is sure to have come on from that and deserves a lot more respect this time on a track he knows well. UNDER TWENTY TWO (1) comes through the same race, where he was also resuming. Needed that hitout and is a likely improver now. Carries the big weight but is worth keeping safe with Mallyon sticking.
